  "modmenu.descriptionTranslation.assist-excavation": "A client-side mining assistant. Toggle it on (default J) to auto-mine the blocks around you in your chosen shape — rectangle, sphere, tunnel (branch mining), or vein (ore-following). Quality-of-life features: auto-switch to the fastest tool for each block, a durability guard that auto-restocks a fresh tool from your inventory before one breaks, protection for Silk Touch / Fortune tools and for containers/spawners, an optional auto-bridge so you don't fall, a Lava Guard that caps nearby lava sources so you don't burn, a configurable inter-block delay, and a preview overlay of what will be mined. A Server-Safe mode disables the detectable techniques. It stays within your normal block-reach and does not break server interaction limits, but a server may still flag automation as cheating — use at your own risk."
